# Format: <file-pattern> <github-username-or-team>
#
# Examples:
#   * @default-reviewer                    - Reviews everything
#   /client/ @frontend-person              - Reviews frontend code
#   /server/ @backend-person               - Reviews backend code
#   *.yml @devops-person                   - Reviews config files
